title: Add-List
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. And User Click Add List Button
4. And User Input Board List
5. And User Click Board List Button
6. Then Verify Success Add List
7. Then Close Web

title: Add-Card
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. And User Click Add Card Button
4. And User Input Card
5. And User Click New Card Button
6. Then Verify Success Add Card

title: Set-Complete-List-Card
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. And User Click Dot Three Card Name
4. And User Click Set Complete List Card
5. Then Verify Complete Card is Success
6. Then Close Web

title: Open-Menu-Board
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. Then Close Web

title: Add-Empty-Card
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. And User Click Add Card Button
4. And User Click New Card Button
5. Then Verify Card Name Cant Empty

title: Add-Empty-Card-List
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle
2. When User Click Board Menu
3. And User Click Add List Button
4. And User Click Board List Button
5. Then Verify List Cant Empty
6. Then Close Web
